name: The Man Who Fell to Earth
description:
"The Man Who Fell to Earth"

A self-portrait in celebration of 666 followers @LimnDigital.

Very much like David Bowie's character in the 1976 film, "The Man Who Fell to Earth" I landed in Madrid, New Mexico (where the film was shot) in 1994. Living & working in New Mexico (with a 16 year side-life in Hawaii from 2002 to 2018) changed me in ways I could not have imagined when I left behind my Iowa farm boy life.
